To locate an article, first go to the "Articles" tab in the navigation bar. You will see 
articles organized into modules listed below.

<%= image_tag "help/articles.png", alt: "Articles Page", class: "img-fluid" %>

To refine your search, you can use both the search bar and the categories filter menu. 
In the search bar, enter a keyword and then click the blue rectangular "Search" button 
to filter out any unrelated articles. In the categories filter menu, you can select or 
deselect checkboxes and then click the blue rectangular "Filter" button to display only 
the articles that match your criteria.
